{"tid":1619030,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"係要反對濫用緊急法，唔係蒙面法","createTime":"2019-10-04T07:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T07:12:57.000Z","uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8393623c82565da29547b7d565dae0726125b9","tid":1619030,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"大家要搞清楚，政府立乜法都要經立法會，包括送中、蒙面惡法<br />\n<br />\n但緊急法一經濫用處理政治事件，特首以後所有惡法都可以自己一個人話事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap241&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7Tod5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=e94eed02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241</a><br />\n在行政長官會同行政會議認為屬緊急情況或危害公安的情況時，行政長官會同行政會議可訂立<span style=\"color: red;\">任何他認為合乎公眾利益的規例</span>。"},{"pid":"dc331aac720bc4cddf2faa1d79dcf1d31c2b8515","tid":1619030,"uid":312150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"兩個都反 冇衝突"}]}